<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>As API Doc says getLocale() should return a Zend_Locale instance. Instead it returns a string like 'de_DE'.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$locale = $translate-&gt;getLocale();
Zend_Debug::dump(is_object($locale)); #returns false;
Zend_Debug::dump(is_string($locale)); #returns true;
$lang = $locale-&gt;toString();  #Fatal error: Call to a member function toString() on a non-object
</code></pre>

